# Environment Configuration

Create a `.env` file in the root directory with the following variables:

```
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_generative_ai_api_key_here
LLM_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=150
PORT=8000
```

Replace `your_google_generative_ai_key_here` with your actual Google Generative AI API key.

## For Render Deployment

Set these as environment variables in your Render dashboard:
- `GOOGLE_API_KEY`: Your Google Generative AI API key
- `LLM_TIMEOUT_SECONDS`: 150 (or adjust as needed)
- `PORT`: Will be automatically set by Render

## Getting a Google Generative AI API Key

1. Go to [Google AI Studio](https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey)
2. Sign in with your Google account
3. Create a new API key
4. Copy the key and use it in your environment variables
